snippet.title: IFSCL 4.0.X Trailer [ Code Lyoko Game ]
snippet.description:
PLAY THE GAME: http://bit.ly/websiteIFSCL
Story Mode chapter 1 got released on June 6th 2020, in version 4.0.4 :
Discord: http://bit.ly/discordIFSCL

Facebook: http://bit.ly/facebookIFSCL

After months of anticipation, this trailer invites you to see glimpses of the first chapter of the story mode but also general content from the update that will come into the well known sandbox mode.

When lot of work is backed up by lot of support, I can go along with it :)
Thank you!

Music used: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X8DO1VBZ-P0
Come and help me to take more time on creating those awesome trailers and making of by supporting me on Patreon: http://bit.ly/patreonIFSCL
